    <section class="aims_objective" id="aims_objective">
        <div class="inner_aims_obj_container">
            <div class="aims-obj_header">
                <img src="https://sanatandharmafoundation.org/wp-content/themes/sanatan-dharma-foundation/assets/images/bullseye.png" alt="icons">
                <h1>Aims and objectives</h1>
            </div>
            <p>As per the Trust Deed of the Foundation, the following are the aims and objectives:</p>
            <h2>Aims</h2>
            <div class="aims_container">
                                                    <div class="aims_box" >
                        <p><b>To research and disseminate knowledge</b> about the philosophy of Sanatan Dharma.</p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box"  style="background-color: #f7d5b9;" >
                        <p><strong>To build a place of pilgrimage</strong> based on the philosophy of Sanatan Dharma.</p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box" >
                        <p>Place of pilgrimage to have <strong>all kind of facilities</strong> that the Trustees deem fit.</p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box"  style="background-color: #f7d5b9;" >
                        <p>To work for the <b>Resurgence of Sanatan Dharma.</b></p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box"  style="background-color: #f7d5b9;" >
                        <p>To contribute in <b>building the character of the people</b> at large.</p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box" >
                        <p>To become a <b>central body for issuing guidelines</b> for way of life following Sanatan Dharma</p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box"  style="background-color: #f7d5b9;" >
                        <p>To have <b>interface with believers of other religions /</b> faiths for peaceful co-existence</p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box" >
                        <p><b>To inculcate pride in Hindu customs,</b> traditions, way of worship, festivals, rituals etc.</p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box" >
                        <p>To create teachers who shall educate coming generations on Sanatan Dharma.</p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box"  style="background-color: #f7d5b9;" >
                        <p>To <b>educate on Sanatan Dharma philosophy</b> and way of living and demonstrate that the world is one big family.</p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box" >
                        <p>To do any kind of charitable activity that the Trustees deem fit in the fields of education, uplifting of women and girl child.</p>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="aims_box"  style="background-color: #f7d5b9;" >
                        <p><b>Supporting younger generation for setting up businesses/</b>professions, healthcare, agriculture, horticulture or in any other field or activity</p>
                    </div>
                            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Objective Start -->
            <section class="objective_container">
                <div class="inner_obj_box">
                <h1>Objectives</h1>
                <p id="top_p">To achieve the above Aims, the Trust shall have following Objectives:</p>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p><strong>To organize debates,</strong> discussions, seminars, campaigns, symposiums and lectures for aims and objectives of Trust.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p><strong>To create awakening</strong> among people of India and world at large about Sanatan Dharma.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p>To support individuals, institutions, organizations who can help in achieving the aims and objectives of the Trust</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p>To initiate a process of establishing an <strong>effective deterrence structure</strong> for people following Sanatan Dharma against those who disturb the peaceful living of followers of Sanatan Dharma.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p><strong>To form committees</strong> of experts to examine critically and draft its outlook on all matters of State policy and existing regulations affecting Trust, its aims, objectives and activities.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p><strong>To work with the State</strong> &amp; Central Governments for achieving the aims and objectives of the Trust.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p><strong>To co-operate, interact and collaborate</strong> and exchange information, advice and any other help required with nation and international agencies, government and non- governmental bodies, organisations, institutions and individuals for achieving and/or furthering the aims and objectives o</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p><strong>To create feeling of Indian oneness</strong> and unity among masses irrespective of caste, creed, religion, colour, language, region and instil national moral and pride.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p><strong>To invite resident Indians,</strong> non-resident Indians, persons of Indian origin and others to join hands in achieving the aims and objectives of the Trust.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p><strong>To spread the message</strong> to the populace of the country to be responsible citizens.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p>To publish, co-operate in or promote the <strong>publication of books, videos,</strong> films, tapes, pamphlets, journals, newssheets etc. for furthering the aims and objectives of the Trust.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p><strong>To disseminate information</strong> through electronic and social media platforms.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p><strong>To do charitable activities</strong> in the fields of education, healthcare, economic upliftment of weaker sections, girl child and women, assisting in start-up businesses, research and production strategy in agriculture/horticulture, set up cow shelter, dairy plants or in any other field or</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p>To do all such other acts that shall further the attainment of aims and objectives of the Trust.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="inner-objct">
                        <div class="circle"></div>
                        <div class="objct-content">
                            <p>To set up its office and create facilities for the officials and Trustees that work for the attainment of aims and objectives of the Trust.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
