    <section class="promotar_profile" id="promotar">
        <div class="inner_promotar">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Promoter Profile</h1>
<h4>Sudesh Aggarwal</h4>
<h4>Chairman &#8211; Board of Trustees</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="promoter_box">
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://sanatandharmafoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/project-founder.jpg" alt="Project Founder" /></p>
<div class="pomoter_content">
<h2>A Brief Profile</h2>
<p>The real-life story of Sudesh Aggarwal is not only inspirational but worthy of emulating. Coming from a lower middle-class family he has risen to feature in a book titled “Top 25 Indian (NRI) Luminaries of the World” along with the likes of top personalities of the world due to his growth in business and social and political engagements in India. He has shown that how by sheer hard work and persistent efforts one can succeed in life without compare</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="pro_content">
<p>Sudesh Aggarwal is the Founder Chairman and Managing Director of Giant Group of Industries with diversified business interests primarily in manufacturing established since 1989. He did Masters in Business Administration in 1973 and his career started as a Management Consultant with Price Waterhouse International subsidiary in Kuwait.</p>
<p>Mr. Aggarwal is the Chairman of India Trade and Exhibition Centre m.e., Former Chairman of Indian Business &amp; Professional Council-Sharjah and Board Member and Sector Chairman-Investments of Business Leaders Forum. His name appears in top 100 Indian businessmen in GCC in Forbes and Arabian Business list.</p>
<p>Mr. Aggarwal devotes his time, other than overlooking business, in managing several not-for-profit organizations in UAE and India in the service of community and his motherland.</p>
<p>He is currently engaged in the study of Sanatan Dharma and is engaged in writing a book describing values, duties and responsibilities enshrined in Sanatan Dharma scriptures together with our culture and traditions. This will be a valuable reference book for Hindus who are followers of Sanatan Dharma and for the parents to pass on knowledge to coming generations.</p>
<p>His dream is to set up a Sanatan Dharma Holy City spread over an area of 10,000 acres (40 sq kilometer) in near future.</p>
</div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="books_container">
        <div class="inner_books_box">
            <div class="books_content">
                <h1>Sudesh Aggarwal In Books</h1>
                <div class="books_image">
                                            <img src="https://sanatandharmafoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/books.png" alt="book">
                                            <img src="https://sanatandharmafoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/books1.png" alt="book">
                                        
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="trusted_deed_section" id="truste">
        <div class="inner_trusted_container">
            <h1>Trust Deed</h1>
            <p>Foundation has been setup via a Trust Deed as per details below:</p>
<div class="trust_inforamation">
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
